ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of MONA KUMAR of Mississauga, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Immigration at Pier 21, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective June 1, 2018, in the place of James Bradley Stafford, whose term has expired.
